transcription.text:
Speaker 1: All right, sir, thank you for your patience.

Speaker 2: I have your account pulled up here, and I do see that you're a VIP status customer. And what was the reason for the cancellation today?

Speaker 1: I have high blood pressure, so I just didn't like how it felt after I took it, so I'm not gonna take it no more.

Speaker 2: I had a stent done in my heart, so I don't wanna take any chances. So I really would like to cancel, please.

Speaker 1: Yeah, absolutely. You didn't feel good when you took it?

Speaker 2: Yes, I did not.

Speaker 1: I'm sorry to hear that you didn't get the desired results that you wanted. I wanna ensure that you got the new HEV and not the previous generic. Would you be able to read to me what it says on the tablet?

Speaker 2: Well, I'm not at home now, so I couldn't even tell what it is. But again, I'm not gonna put my life at risk, you know, taking whatever it is. So I would really like to cancel.

Speaker 1: Okay, sir, not a problem. I've gone ahead and I've canceled any future orders.

Speaker 2: Okay, sir?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: You're all set, I've canceled your account.

Speaker 1: All right, perfect, thank you very much.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye.
